  <brief_title>The Association Between Autoimmune or Inflammation and Thyroid Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Relationship of Vascular Cell Adhesion Molecule 1, C-reactive Protein, Brain-derived Neurotrophic Factor, Orexin and Depressive Symptoms in the Subjects With Thyroid Disease</official_title>
