  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims to evaluate the effects of thyroid functions on energy homeostasis and
      inflammation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The subjects were enrolled for evaluation of thyroid functions. The associations between
      thyroid function and energy homeostasis and inflammation will be assessed.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
